  ('locality-8b44517b-moex-00249', 'locality-8b44517b', 'locality-8b44517b-moex-110-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-8b44517b-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '如果需求是具有彈性的，那麼下列何者正確？', '["價格效果大於數量效果，價格的下降將導致總收入增加", "價格效果大於數量效果，價格的增加將導致總收入增加", "數量效果大於價格效果，價格的增加將導致總收入增加", "數量效果大於價格效果，價格的下降將導致總收入增加"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93d510670c35", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35a08a6bdee2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "305", "s": "1302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-8b44517b-moex-00250', 'locality-8b44517b', 'locality-8b44517b-moex-110-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-locality-8b44517b-06', NULL, 'single_choice', '在其他條件不變情況下，廠商增加僱用員工使得它的邊際產量上升，則該廠商的：', '["短期平均總成本小於邊際成本", "短期平均變動成本大於邊際成本", "短期平均總成本上升", "邊際成本上升"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:32+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "93d510670c35", "answer_pdf_sha1": "35a08a6bdee2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "305", "s": "1302", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "勞工行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
